      "paragraphs": [
        "Join Us on the Journey Towards Success",
        "Get in touch with us today to book your FREE discovery session where we will evaluate your requirements.",
        "We work with you to craft a tailored plan for building a new data warehouse or optimizing your existing one.",
        "We design, develop, & implement your data warehouse solution, for you to enjoy quicker access to quality data, business-wide."
      ],
